AOP-Aspect Oriented Programming
AOP is a programming approach used to separate cross-cutting concerns from business logic.
Oops as Classes likewise AOP as aspects
AOP allo us to focus on Business logic by handling boilerplate and repatative code like logging, Transaction managemnet etc.
Helps in achieving reusabality, maintainability of the code.


These are functionalities that are needed across many modules, like:
Logging
Security
Transaction management
Exception handling
Performance monitoring
âŒ Without AOP â†’ repeated code everywhere
âœ… With AOP â†’ centralized & clean code


we need to add dependency inside our POM>XML
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-aop</artifactId>
</dependency>
